text: “phwk cea ca mi txsu kranan hrux sung klum chn thi thalay khaman sayya khxng phwk khea læa mung khab li rx sul hı xxk pi thang «thi phwk khea di reim ptibati kæ phwk cea kxn pen khrang ræk phwk cea klaw phwk khea kranan hrux? Xallxh tanghak lea khux phu thi smkhwr kæ kar thi phwk cea ca klaw hak phwk cea pen phu sraththa
